    "Finally, ChatGPT is still being trained through the queries and responses.",
    "So, this model is updated (with new data and algorithms) to generate innovative responses.• Improve data analysis and interpretation: The text summarizing capability of ChatGPT can help researchers with a better understanding of existing knowledge on a specific topic.",
    "ChatGPT can analyze large data sets refined from a large number of texts without human involvement [56] which in turn may produce interesting patterns that can be difficult to reveal through traditional approaches to data analysis.",
