    "(b) Education and knowledge retrieval: ChatGPT can be used as an educational tool to assist students as well as teachers in retrieving knowledge and information:• Enhance collaboration and peer learning: ChatGPT's sophisticated language processing abilities can facilitate cross-field collaboration that may enable students from diverse disciplines to communicate and collaborate more effectively [22] The model's ability to answer questions and provide information can encourage knowledge sharing and peer-to-peer learning among students."
